#31400
A Beaten Path in the Forest~
   You are on a well worn path made by some large hooved animal.  The ground
is mostly pine needles and leaves from the trees surrounding the path.  At the
center of the path the ground is soft, and black soil peeks through in some
places.  Your exits are west back to the open forest and east further in the
path.  
