#31420
Bend in a Dimly Lit Passage~
   The light from torches that flicker along the walls is brighter here, but
still dim.  The mortared stone and wooden beam passage continues here and a
bend leads to the east.  The distinct scent of people can be detected here
along with smells of food.  Footsteps echo on the hard packed dirt floor of
the passageway.  
