#31423
A Wide Hallway in the Stronghold~
   The passageway opens into a large hallway with doorways that flank each
side.  The doorways on both sides directly east and west are framed with the
same large wooden beams.  Animal hides have been hung to provide a door of
some sort for each room.  Large torches flicker between the doorways in
addition to the light that radiates from the chandelier directly southward.  
