#31424
Stronghold Armory~
   This expansive room is filled with heaps of armor and weapons.  A large
candle fixture is suspended from the wooden ceiling beams and holds several
lit candles that illuminate the room.  The light from the candles flickers on
the heaps of loosely organized armor.  The northern wall is lined with hooks
that suits of heavy leather armor hangs from.  On the southern wall hang weapons
from axes to two-handed swords that seem to only be made for giants.  A dark
wooden shelf with three levels spans the entire eastern wall and is packed
with various helms, some with horns welded on the sides.  A large wooden chair
sits in the northwestern corner pointed towards the door, as if the occupant
would be on guard and watching the entrance at all times.  
~
314 76 0 0 0 0
D3
~
~
