#31427
Seidr's Quarters~
   Behind the pristine white animal hide, this room is lit by an altar at the
far eastern wall.  Candles in various stages of burning flicker brightly and
some are lit in different hues of orange and red giving the room an ethereal
quality.  A large pillow, made of stuffed animal hide, lies in the center of
the room.  A small wooden table sits at the southern wall with various
instruments used for writing and etchings.  Runes are carved into the walls at
various symmetrical points on each wall.  Some of these runes almost seem to
glow.  
~
