#31428
High Priest's Chamber~
   Behind the thick hide that serves as the curtain, this room may be the
cleanest in the entire stronghold.  The well-packed dirt floor is nearly
polished here and torches are set in each corner of the room to provide ample
light.  Depictions of Freya, Odin, and other gods are depicted in etchings on
each wall.  A large table sits at the northern wall with several bound books
neatly stacked on the surface.  The smell of burning sage comes from a brass
thurible hanging from a hook over the table.  
~
