#31430
Barracks of the Berserkers~
   Pallets line the northern and southern walls of this expansive room.  
They are covered in thick animal furs that were made to fight the bitter cold
of this climate.  This is the quarters of the male fighters in the stronghold.
Torches line the walls, but only two on the western wall are actually lit,
casting a dim glow to the entire room.  On the western wall between the
torches is an intricate depiction of Thor in a battle stance.  
~
