#31433
Center of the War Room~
   This room is wide open to the left and right with ceilings double the
height of the rest of the stronghold.  The room is nearly overcome by the size
of the expansive wooden table that extends nearly from the east wall to the
west wall.  A large map of the North lies on the table with wooden figurines
stationed strategically, clearly in the midst of an attack plan.  Large wooden
chairs with straight backs are tucked into the table here, and an enormous
candle fixture hands from brass chains over the center of the table to light
the room.  To the north, behind an extremely large chair is another room
behind a fur-lined curtain.  
~
