Jarl's Quarters~
   This room has a pallet that is double the size found in either of the
barracks and is lined with luxurious furs that appear to be extremely warm.  
The walls are lined with tapestries depicting many battles including those in
which gods such as Odin participated.  The eastern wall holds a large table
with a chair tucked under and several empty ivory mugs sit atop.  The bleached
skull of the extinct tundra wolf, triple the size of a typical wolf's skull,
is mounted in the center of the northern wall.  
