Provisions Cache~
   This room was dug out carefully and the dirt packed tightly and supported
with the same wooden beams that make up the rest of the stronghold.  Shelves
line every wall and are filled with dried fruits, meat, and vegetables.  
Onions and garlic are tied together and suspended from a beam that runs from
wall to wall.  A wooden ladder leads back up into the war room.  
